thread.title: BRIEF-Gohigh Data Networks Technology sees FY 2017 net profit to raise to 160 mln yuan to 195 mln yuan

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Gohigh Data Networks Technology sees FY 2017 net profit to raise to 160 mln yuan to 195 mln yuan

organizations.name: gohigh data networks technology co ltd

text:
Jan 10(Reuters) - Gohigh Data Networks Technology Co Ltd
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to raise to 160 million yuan to 195 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 80.1 million yuan (before restructuring)
* Says investment income from sale of Beijing-based payment technology firm is the main reason for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/iugtGV
